Just got gemini to have a look at the embed code,
It suggested this:
```document.addEventListener('hs-form-event:on-submission:success', function(event) {
  // Access details about the form submission from the event object
  const formId = event.detail.formId;
  const instanceId = event.detail.instanceId;

  // Run your custom code here
  console.log(`Form with ID ${formId} and instance ID ${instanceId} was submitted successfully!`);
  // Add your custom logic here, e.g., display a thank you message,
  // redirect to another page, or update page content.
});```
